#20200
Academy Entrance~
@@NYou stand in the grand entrance hall of the @@WAcademy of Adventure@@N.
Tall stone pillars rise to a vaulted ceiling above.  Torchlight flickers
across carved murals depicting heroes in battle, explorers navigating
dungeons, and merchants haggling over goods.  A large sign hangs on the
wall, welcoming new adventurers.
The path continues @@ynorth@@N deeper into the academy.
~
1032 11
D0
You see a long hallway stretching into the academy.
~
~
0 0 20201
D2
You see the familiar glow of the temple.
~
~
0 -1 3001
E
sign~
@@W*** Welcome to the Academy of Adventure! ***@@N

This academy will teach you everything you need to survive in the world.
Read the @@Wsigns@@N in each room carefully -- they contain vital lessons.

To read a sign, type '@@yLOOK SIGN@@N'.

When you are ready, go @@yNORTH@@N to begin your training.

~
S
#20201
Lesson I: Movement~
@@NYou are in a wide corridor with smooth stone walls.  Faded tapestries
depicting maps of the world hang on either side.  A large sign is mounted
on the wall here.  Exits lead @@ynorth@@N, @@yeast@@N, and @@ysouth@@N.
~
