sign~
@@WLesson VIII: Shopping@@N

When you are in a shop, you can buy and sell items:

  @@yLIST@@N           -- See what the shopkeeper has for sale
  @@yBUY <item>@@N     -- Purchase an item
  @@ySELL <item>@@N    -- Sell an item to the shopkeeper
  @@yVALUE <item>@@N   -- See how much the shopkeeper will pay for your item

Try '@@yLIST@@N' to see what is available, then '@@yBUY BREAD@@N' and
'@@yBUY FLASK@@N'.

To eat and drink:

  @@yEAT <food>@@N     -- Eat something to satisfy hunger
  @@yDRINK <drink>@@N  -- Drink something to quench thirst

When ready, go @@ySOUTH@@N.

~
