sign~
@@WLesson IX: Combat@@N

Before fighting, always check how tough a monster is:

  @@yCONSIDER <mob>@@N  -- Compare your strength to a monster

To fight:

  @@yKILL <mob>@@N      -- Attack a monster
  @@yFLEE@@N            -- Try to escape from combat
  @@yWIMPY <number>@@N  -- Auto-flee when your HP drops below this number

@@RIMPORTANT:@@N Below this room is a @@RTOUGH@@N monster in a cage.  Go @@yDOWN@@N
to practice fighting and fleeing.  Type '@@yCONSIDER BLOB@@N' first, then
'@@yKILL BLOB@@N', then '@@yFLEE@@N' when your health gets low!

After practicing fleeing, come back here and go @@yWEST@@N to the trials.

~
S
