@@WRemember:@@N
  @@yRECALL@@N  -- Teleport back to the temple at any time
  @@ySAVE@@N    -- Save your character (auto-saves every few minutes)
  @@yHELP@@N    -- Get help on any topic
  @@yWHO@@N     -- See who else is playing
  @@yQUIT@@N    -- Leave the game (your character is saved)

May your adventures be legendary!

~
